node.text: A finale that you won’t want to miss. There’s no better way to celebrate #RamboDay than to reserve your seat to #Rambo: Last Blood - In theaters FRIDAY. Link in bio.

node.text: Good luck on trying to figure out where this is from. KeepPunching.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sly Stallone on September 17, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'Exclusive: Nighthawks: Sylvester Stallone classic to become a limited series with Frank Grillo! BY CHRIS BUMBRAY 4DAYSAGO 29% Nighthawk Best Movie You.'.

node.text: Oh I’m very happy to be involved with this from beginning to end. And we are incredibly fortunate to have Frank Grillo playing  the lead. He’ll be fantastic!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sly Stallone on September 10, 2021 tagging @sistinestallone, @scarletstallone, and @sophiastallone. May be an image of 4 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text: As you go down the road of life the hardest part is saying goodbye to the family for extended periods of time. It doesn’t get easier. Getting ready to go back to work already I miss my wonderful daughters and fantastic wife.  Well, keep punching, kids, Dad  shall return soon!

Sometimes it’s very interesting to go back to the “ Starting Line” and remember when the big race began on CAMINO PALMERO  st … For me it was buckling down, and setting my mind to a task that far exceeded all my dreams and expectations. I must  thank you all for that.  This is why you must never stop Punching , Sly

node.text: I came across this very rare photo that I’ve never seen it before. It just reminded me of a old fight poster from 100 years ago. Well, I just saw the NEW trailer for the new directors cut of Rocky IV , And in my humble estimation it is amazing.  Great work by the trailer editors! This battle, with the new footage is extraordinary.  Premiering in Philadelphia November 11! @mgmstudios @dolphlundgren @sly.stallone1976
